OL,3,CBeyond the fairytale: What is next for
OL,4,CLeicester City?
OL,6,FIt's far from the days of dilly ding
OL,7,Fdilly dongs, Jamie Vardy parties, and
OL,8,Fchatting rubbish and getting...well,
OL,9,Fyou know the rest.
OL,11,FTen years ago, they were of course
OL,12,FPremier League winners, and now
OL,13,Fthey're League One punters. Relegated
OL,14,Fto the third tier for only the second
OL,15,Ftime in their 142 year history.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G1/14
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
