OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F377A1776967869
OL,3,CBeyond the fairytale: What is next for
OL,4,CLeicester City?
OL,6,FThe fairytale and the dream hasn't
OL,7,Fjust ended for Leicester, it has
OL,8,Fbecome a nightmare. Filled with points
OL,9,Fdeductions, fall outs, and fan dismay.
OL,10,FIt is no understatement to say that
OL,11,Fthe club faces a real identity crisis.
OL,13,FThe question isn't how they climbed
OL,14,Fthe mountain or how they fell off it,
OL,15,Fbut rather what happens next?
OL,17,FThe club hierarchy
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G2/14
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
