PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F377A1776967869
OL,3,CBeyond the fairytale: What is next for
OL,4,CLeicester City?
OL,6,FThe Srivaddhanaprabha family were once
OL,7,Fconsidered the gold standard of
OL,8,Ffootball ownership, but now they are a
OL,9,Fhouse crumbling under considerable
OL,10,Fpressure.
OL,12,FAfter their match against Hull City,
OL,13,FKhun Top faced questions from the fans
OL,14,Fabout the current model and
OL,15,Fleadership. Many of them believe that
OL,16,Fthose at the top of the club are the
OL,17,Farchitects of this decline.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G3/14
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,378,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37704
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F377A1776967869
OL,3,CBeyond the fairytale: What is next for
OL,4,CLeicester City?
OL,6,FIn a statement released shortly after
OL,7,Ffull time the chairman said that
OL,8,F"there are no excuses" and signalled a
OL,9,Fdesire to rebuild. But the financial
OL,10,Fblueprint for that remains a mystery.
OL,12,FThe finances
OL,14,FThe numbers are sobering. The revenue
OL,15,Ffrom broadcasting alone will decrease
OL,16,Ffrom #12 million to #2 million.
OL,17,FFigures this week appear to show that
OL,18,Fthey have already cashed in on
OL,19,Fparachute payments from the Premier
OL,20,FLeague.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G4/14
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,378,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37705
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F377A1776967869
OL,3,CBeyond the fairytale: What is next for
OL,4,CLeicester City?
OL,6,FLosses are extraordinarily high too.
OL,7,FFootball finance expert Kieran Maguire
OL,8,Fbelieves the club have lost #400
OL,9,Fmillion since 2018. While some loans
OL,10,Ffrom King Power can be written off, it
OL,11,Frepresents a massive hit on the
OL,12,Fowners' personal wealth.
OL,14,FTo survive, Maguire warns of
OL,15,Fsignificant internal redundancies.
OL,16,FWith wages capped at 60% of revenue, a
OL,17,Fshrink is inevitable. It won't just be
OL,18,Fthe players on the pitch, recruitment
OL,19,Fteams and backroom offices will likely
OL,20,Fface the axe.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G5/14
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,378,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37706
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F377A1776967869
OL,3,CBeyond the fairytale: What is next for
OL,4,CLeicester City?
OL,6,FAnd as Maguire warns, we're still to
OL,7,Fhear of any subsequent breaches of
OL,8,Ffinances from the EFL, meaning that
OL,9,Fthe finances could get worse or
OL,10,FLeicester could be faced with another
OL,11,Fpoints deduction.
OL,13,FTo comply with wages and squad rules
OL,14,FLeicester will have to move players
OL,15,Fon. Players such as Harry Winks,
OL,16,FJannik Vestergaard, and Stephy
OL,17,FMavididi will surely all go.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G6/14
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,378,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37707
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F377A1776967869
OL,3,CBeyond the fairytale: What is next for
OL,4,CLeicester City?
OL,6,FThe club currently spends the most
OL,7,Famount of money on wages than any
OL,8,Fother in the Championship. The wages
OL,9,Fwill have to come down and the squad
OL,10,Fwill without doubt look very
OL,11,Fdifferent. Even young players such as
OL,12,FLuke Thomas and Jeremy Monga may have
OL,13,Fto make way.
OL,15,FLooking at the squad in its entirety
OL,16,Fit is likely that only a couple of the
OL,17,Fplayers that lined up against Hull
OL,18,FCity will remain. The XI may look
OL,19,Funrecognisable.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G7/14
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,378,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37708
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F377A1776967869
OL,3,CBeyond the fairytale: What is next for
OL,4,CLeicester City?
OL,6,FThe search for a new leader too starts
OL,7,Fnow, with Gary Rowett departing his
OL,8,Fpost at the end of the season.
OL,10,FThe facilities
OL,12,FThe facilities provide a paradox for
OL,13,FLeicester. On the one hand, players
OL,14,Fwill be drawn to sign for them in the
OL,15,Fthird tier partly because of their
OL,16,Fstate of the art facilities at
OL,17,FSeagrave. On the other, the cost alone
OL,18,Ffor running such facilities might not
OL,19,Fbe financially viable.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G8/14
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,378,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37709
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F377A1776967869
OL,3,CBeyond the fairytale: What is next for
OL,4,CLeicester City?
OL,6,FThe scaling down of the academy, which
OL,7,Fhas produced bright talent at
OL,8,FLeicester, looks inevitable. The
OL,9,Fwomen's team could also be curtailed,
OL,10,Fas Leicester Women look set for
OL,11,Frelegation themselves from the Women's
OL,12,FSuper League.
OL,14,FMaguire warns that all of this would
OL,15,Fbe necessary in an effort to cut and
OL,16,Fkeep down day to day running costs.
OL,18,FThe local area and community
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G9/14
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
