PN,37710
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F377A1776967869
OL,3,CBeyond the fairytale: What is next for
OL,4,CLeicester City?
OL,6,FThe club will be less of an appeal.
OL,7,FWhilst the EFL is popular, it doesn't
OL,8,Fcompare to the finances and bright
OL,9,Flights of the Premier League. The club
OL,10,Fknows that - and the effect of smaller
OL,11,Ffanbases coming to town, which fill
OL,12,Fless of the stadium, could be felt by
OL,13,Fbusinesses around the King Power
OL,14,Fdespite the increased volume of games
OL,15,Ffor teams in League One.
OL,17,FIn terms of Leicester's work in the
OL,18,Flocal community, there will be less
OL,19,Fcash available at the club in general,
OL,20,Fbut there is no indication at this
OL,21,Fstage of any scaling back.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4         G10/14
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
