OL,3,CBeyond the fairytale: What is next for
OL,4,CLeicester City?
OL,6,FFour becomes five
OL,8,FWith relegation to League One the
OL,9,FFoxes join an exclusive club to which
OL,10,Fno-one wants to belong. They are the
OL,11,Ffifth team to suffer back to back
OL,12,Frelegations from the Premier League to
OL,13,FLeague One in consecutive seasons.
OL,14,FThey now sit alongside Wolves,
OL,15,FSunderland, Luton and Swindon.
OL,17,FLooking at each team individually:
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4         G11/14
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
