OL,3,CBeyond the fairytale: What is next for
OL,4,CLeicester City?
OL,6,FLooking at the history, it suggest a
OL,7,Fmulti-year slog in the wilderness. But
OL,8,Fthe Foxes have never been too
OL,9,Finterested in following the script.
OL,11,FWe have in fact seen this film before.
OL,12,FBack in 2009, the club were in the
OL,13,Fthird tier but only for a one season
OL,14,Flay over. And now armed with elite
OL,15,Ffacilities, the club shouldn't
OL,16,Fstruggle to attract players to rebuild.
OL,18,FFor years the Foxes have been the ones
OL,19,Fhunted, but they must rediscover the
OL,20,Fhunger to become the predator again.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4         G12/14
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
