PN,37713
SC,0013
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F377A1776967869
OL,3,CBeyond the fairytale: What is next for
OL,4,CLeicester City?
OL,6,FThe new recruits may have missed the
OL,7,Foriginal fairytale, but can now craft
OL,8,Ftheir own story. It's not about
OL,9,Fmourning the glory days. The story
OL,10,Fisn't over, instead it's just getting
OL,11,Fsecond wind.
OL,13,FFor more on football from across the
OL,14,FMidlands, head to ITVX to watch
OL,15,F'Coventry City: The Resurrection',
OL,16,Ffeaturing exclusive clips with Frank
OL,17,FLampard
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4         G13/14
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
